column5: Hi Guys, I lost my hyper link to EOSDIS to see the snow and ice left up north. Can anyone provide the link? There where multiple views showing snow&ice in Red, and open water in Blue. I love to watch the ice leave my favorite lakes. Thxs in advance. FT
I Google had a satellite and fund it that way
Freaking spell check,I Google nasa satellite and find it there
